Description: Create and integrate maps into your R workflow. It allows various cartographic representation: proportionnal symbols, chroropleth, typology, flow, discontinuities... It also proposes some additional usefull features: cartographic palettes, layout (scale, north arrow, title...), labels, legends, access to cartographic API...
